title: Gianfranco Circati
text:
Gianfranco Circati (born 2 February 1971) is an Italian <a href="association%20football">football</a>er.
Circati played for a number of teams in <a href="Italian%20football%20league%20system">Italian football</a> with the majority of his career being in <a href="Serie%20B">Serie B</a> and <a href="Serie%20C">Serie C</a>, though he did have a stint in <a href="Serie%20A">Serie A</a> with <a href="Parma%20F.C.">Parma F.C.</a>.
